On the grid:
ships have
  size
  armor: array of length [size] with values [BROKEN, NORMAL, SUPER]
  cannons
  radar
  sonar
  position
  speed
  turn zone: list of potential final positions and the empty squares needed to get there
  sunk or not?
  abilities:
    mine pickup/dropoff
    radar increase
    torpedo
mines
base
  radar
  health: array of length [size] with values [BROKEN, NORMAL]
coral
